<text top="35" left="72" width="448" height="11" font="0">This is an unofficial translation of the Resolution and is provided here for information purposes only. </text>
<text top="47" left="72" width="348" height="11" font="0">Reliance may only be placed upon the official Arabic version of the Resolution. </text>
<text top="61" left="108" width="3" height="11" font="1"> </text>
<text top="74" left="108" width="3" height="11" font="1"> </text>
<text top="88" left="108" width="3" height="11" font="1"> </text>
<text top="102" left="108" width="3" height="11" font="1"> </text>
<text top="116" left="108" width="3" height="11" font="1"> </text>
<text top="127" left="138" width="375" height="16" font="2"><b>Regulations on Protection of the Confidentiality and Privacy of </b></text>
<text top="143" left="256" width="103" height="16" font="2"><b>Beneficiary Data </b></text>
<text top="161" left="324" width="3" height="11" font="1"> </text>
<text top="175" left="108" width="3" height="11" font="1"> </text>
<text top="187" left="72" width="52" height="16" font="2"><b>Article 1 </b></text>
<text top="187" left="136" width="136" height="16" font="3">The licensee may request</text>
<text top="186" left="271" width="4" height="16" font="8"> </text>
<text top="187" left="275" width="269" height="16" font="3"> the beneficiary to provide his/her personal data, </text>
<text top="202" left="136" width="408" height="16" font="3">provided that these data are necessary to activate the required service;  the </text>
<text top="218" left="136" width="408" height="16" font="3">Licensee in this case shall keep the beneficiary aware of the purpose  for </text>
<text top="234" left="136" width="408" height="16" font="3">which  those  data  were  collected  and  of  the  possibility  of  processing  or </text>
<text top="250" left="136" width="94" height="16" font="3">preserving them. </text>
<text top="265" left="136" width="14" height="16" font="3">    </text>
<text top="282" left="72" width="53" height="16" font="2"><b>Article 2 </b></text>
<text top="282" left="136" width="408" height="16" font="3">Without prejudice to the licensee’s obligations to ensure protection of the </text>
<text top="297" left="136" width="408" height="16" font="3">confidentiality and privacy of the data  obtained from the beneficiary, the </text>
<text top="313" left="136" width="217" height="16" font="3">licensee shall be abide by the following: </text>
<text top="329" left="136" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="345" left="154" width="9" height="16" font="3">a.</text>
<text top="347" left="163" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="345" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">Process or use beneficiary’s data for their specified purpose in such </text>
<text top="360" left="172" width="334" height="16" font="3">a  manner  that  does  not  contradict  with  the  provisions  of</text>
<text top="363" left="506" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="360" left="512" width="31" height="16" font="3">these </text>
<text top="376" left="172" width="73" height="16" font="3">Regulations.  </text>
<text top="392" left="172" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="408" left="154" width="10" height="16" font="3">b.</text>
<text top="410" left="164" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="408" left="172" width="297" height="16" font="3">Limit the access to the data to the relevant employees. </text>
<text top="423" left="172" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="439" left="154" width="9" height="16" font="3">c.</text>
<text top="441" left="163" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="439" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">Take all technical and professional precautions that are necessary to </text>
<text top="455" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">protect  its  systems  and  networks  ,  and  to  prevent  unauthorised </text>
<text top="471" left="172" width="126" height="16" font="3">access to  these data.    </text>
<text top="486" left="208" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="502" left="154" width="10" height="16" font="3">d.</text>
<text top="504" left="164" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="502" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">Issue  a  regulation,  approved  by  the  Authority,  of  the  procedures </text>
<text top="518" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">followed to protect confidentiality and privacy of these data. This </text>
<text top="534" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">regulation  shall  be  published  on  the  Licensee’s  website  and  the </text>
<text top="549" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">beneficiary  shall  receive  a  copy  from  the  Licensee  when  applying </text>
<text top="565" left="172" width="84" height="16" font="3">for the service. </text>
<text top="581" left="208" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="597" left="154" width="9" height="16" font="3">e.</text>
<text top="599" left="163" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="597" left="172" width="274" height="16" font="3">Update the beneficiary’s data whenever necessary. </text>
<text top="612" left="208" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="628" left="154" width="8" height="16" font="3">f.</text>
<text top="630" left="161" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="628" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">Inform  the  beneficiary  of  the  person  or  entity  s/he  can  obtain </text>
<text top="644" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">his/her  information  from    and  of  the  period  of  time  for  keeping </text>
<text top="660" left="172" width="68" height="16" font="3">such data.    </text>
<text top="675" left="208" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="691" left="172" width="9" height="16" font="3">g.</text>
<text top="693" left="181" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="691" left="208" width="335" height="16" font="3">Keep  the  beneficiary  informed  of  any  breaches  or  security </text>
</page>
<page number="3" position="absolute" top="0" left="0" height="792" width="612">
<text top="35" left="72" width="448" height="11" font="0">This is an unofficial translation of the Resolution and is provided here for information purposes only. </text>
<text top="47" left="72" width="348" height="11" font="0">Reliance may only be placed upon the official Arabic version of the Resolution. </text>
<text top="61" left="108" width="3" height="11" font="1"> </text>
<text top="74" left="108" width="3" height="11" font="1"> </text>
<text top="86" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">threats affect or probably have a negative impact on the integrity of </text>
<text top="102" left="172" width="344" height="16" font="3">his/her data or could lead to exposing the data to a third party. </text>
<text top="118" left="208" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="133" left="172" width="10" height="16" font="3">h.</text>
<text top="135" left="182" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="133" left="208" width="336" height="16" font="3">Permit the Authority to access or disclose  the beneficiary’s </text>
<text top="149" left="172" width="356" height="16" font="3">data, if this is required pursuant to the Telecommunications Act.  </text>
<text top="165" left="172" width="7" height="16" font="3">  </text>
<text top="181" left="172" width="6" height="16" font="3">i.</text>
<text top="183" left="178" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="181" left="208" width="336" height="16" font="3">Cancel  or  block  any    data  that  are  inconsistent  with  the </text>
<text top="196" left="172" width="180" height="16" font="3">provisions of these Regulations.  </text>
<text top="212" left="136" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="228" left="72" width="53" height="16" font="2"><b>Article 3 </b></text>
<text top="228" left="136" width="408" height="16" font="3">Following a written approval of the beneficiary, the Licensee is permitted </text>
<text top="244" left="136" width="408" height="16" font="3">to publish or exchange the beneficiary`s data with any of its subsidiaries or </text>
<text top="260" left="136" width="407" height="16" font="3">with  any  other  companies.  In  such  case  the  licensee  is  obliged  to </text>
<text top="276" left="136" width="52" height="16" font="3">guarantee</text>
<text top="276" left="188" width="4" height="16" font="2"><b> </b></text>
<text top="276" left="193" width="117" height="16" font="3">not to use these data</text>
<text top="276" left="310" width="4" height="16" font="2"><b> </b></text>
<text top="276" left="315" width="40" height="16" font="3">for any</text>
<text top="276" left="355" width="4" height="16" font="2"><b> </b></text>
<text top="276" left="359" width="184" height="16" font="3">purpose other than the specified </text>
<text top="291" left="136" width="245" height="16" font="3">purposes   and within the permissible limits.  </text>
<text top="308" left="72" width="53" height="16" font="2"><b>Article 4 </b></text>
<text top="308" left="136" width="408" height="16" font="3">The beneficiary may, in order to ensure protection of the confidentiality </text>
<text top="323" left="136" width="321" height="16" font="3">and privacy of his/her data, take   the following measures:  </text>
<text top="339" left="154" width="9" height="16" font="3">a.</text>
<text top="341" left="163" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="339" left="172" width="375" height="16" font="3">Access  his/her data from the directory or the website and request  </text>
<text top="355" left="172" width="227" height="16" font="3">amendment or cancelation of these data.  </text>
<text top="371" left="154" width="10" height="16" font="3">b.</text>
<text top="373" left="164" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="371" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">Appeal to the Authority in case the Licensee is in breach of these </text>
<text top="386" left="172" width="70" height="16" font="3">Regulations. </text>
<text top="403" left="72" width="53" height="16" font="2"><b>Article 5 </b></text>
<text top="403" left="136" width="128" height="16" font="3">The Licensee shall not: </text>
<text top="418" left="136" width="7" height="16" font="3">  </text>
<text top="434" left="154" width="9" height="16" font="3">a.</text>
<text top="436" left="163" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="434" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">Lease  or  sell  the  beneficiary’s  data  to  any  person  or  entity  that  is </text>
<text top="450" left="172" width="356" height="16" font="3">not engaged in providing the services required by the beneficiary. </text>
<text top="466" left="172" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="481" left="154" width="10" height="16" font="3">b.</text>
<text top="483" left="164" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="481" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3"> Require the beneficiary to provide data that are not relevant to the </text>
<text top="497" left="172" width="119" height="16" font="3">provision of services. </text>
<text top="513" left="136" width="10" height="16" font="3">   </text>
<text top="529" left="154" width="9" height="16" font="3">c.</text>
<text top="531" left="163" width="4" height="13" font="9"> </text>
<text top="528" left="172" width="4" height="16" font="8"> </text>
<text top="529" left="175" width="368" height="16" font="3">Without prejudice to any obligations on the Licensee  according to </text>
<text top="544" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">its license, retain the beneficiary’s data for a period exceeding three </text>
<text top="560" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">months from the date of expiry of the contract. Upon the expiry of </text>
<text top="576" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">the  aforementioned  period, such  data  shall  be  stored  in  databases </text>
<text top="592" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">that  are  not  accessible  by  the  licensee.  The  Authority  shall </text>
<text top="607" left="172" width="261" height="16" font="3">determine the party that may access these data.  </text>
<text top="623" left="208" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="639" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">The  Authority  may  extend  that  period  if  it  is  satisfied  that  the </text>
<text top="655" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">licensee’s application is  grounded, provided  that  the  beneficiary  is </text>
<text top="670" left="172" width="60" height="16" font="3">informed.  </text>
<text top="686" left="136" width="4" height="16" font="3"> </text>
<text top="702" left="172" width="372" height="16" font="3">d. Exchange beneficiary’s data across borders with any person, firm </text>
</page>
